                  FOR COLLABORATIONS:
   AS A TEAM LEADER:
   On IntelliJ:
   File -> Project -> VCS -> Enable Version Control -> .gitignore (.out, .idea) -> Commit changes -> VCS -> Import into Version Control -> Share Project on GitHub
   
   On GHW:
   The Project -> Settings -> Manage Access -> invite collaborators by their username
   !!! if the team sees the project & Add File on their site -> all is well.
   
   AS A COLLABORATOR:
   !!! join the invitation on by email
   On IntelliJ:
   File -> Project From Version Control -> Copy URL (on the invitation email OR from the green CODE button on GHW) and Paste -> Clone
                  
